&lt;p&gt;base64 解密题目：Is this base?&lt;br&gt;
flag.txt 里：&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/40371717/1711628286956-33e4e3d1-457e-4c1b-bd10-c95a47f92cbe.png#averageHue=%23efedeb&amp;amp;clientId=u579708c9-233f-4&amp;amp;from=paste&amp;amp;height=336&amp;amp;id=u232577d4&amp;amp;originHeight=420&amp;amp;originWidth=617&amp;amp;originalType=binary&amp;amp;ratio=1.25&amp;amp;rotation=0&amp;amp;showTitle=false&amp;amp;size=38109&amp;amp;status=done&amp;amp;style=none&amp;amp;taskId=uc372cf0a-63f9-4b2b-b261-c45f3c09c1f&amp;amp;title=&amp;amp;width=493.6&#34; alt=&#34;image.png&#34;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
